name: urmom
description: Specifically created for the pulsechain network. This is a pure meme coin with 50.5% of the supply burned myself to the pulsechain burn address. This was my sole motivation for the pulsechain version with a large burn of LP and Dev supply to protect the chart and holders. AMEN.
